	      <img class="media-object" src="/images/notifications/timed-trigger-calm-technology.png" alt="Timed Trigger Calm Technology">
	    </a>
	    <div class="media-body">
	      <h4 class="media-heading">Timed Trigger</h4>
	      <p>A simple status light on a timer can make for a calm and informative notifier.</p>
	      <p>An orange light that turns on at sundown or reminds you to brush your teeth.</p>
	    </div>
	  </li>
	</ul>

</div> 

