	      <img class="media-object" src="/images/notifications/delay-example-calm-technology.png" alt="Delay Calm Technology">
	    </a>
	    <div class="media-body">
	      <h4 class="media-heading">Delay</h4>
	      <p>Use a delay or interrupt during a change of state.</p>
	      <p>For example, when the headphones of an iPhone become disconnected, the music player automatically pauses the music.</p>
